:GRAPH TOT_CAP
:TITLE TOT_CAP
:SCALE
:VAR tot cap WF12
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 3.5e+006
:SCALE
:VAR total capacity of installed wind turbines
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 3.5e+006

:GRAPH JOBS
:TITLE JOBS
:X-MIN 2019
:X-MAX 2020
:SCALE
:VAR total jobs per MW
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR total jobs per MW corrected
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR total jobs per sales
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR total jobs per sales corrected
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR total jobs WF12
:LINE-WIDTH 1

:GRAPH USER2
:TITLE USER2
:SCALE
:VAR world electricity demand
:Y-MIN 15000
:Y-MAX 30000
:SCALE
:VAR world electricity supply
:Y-MIN 15000
:Y-MAX 30000

:GRAPH CO2
:TITLE CO2
:SCALE
:VAR cumulative CO2 emissions avoided
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 1e+010
:SCALE
:VAR cumulative CO2 emissions avoided cte
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 1e+010
:SCALE
:VAR cumulative CO2 emissions avoided WF12
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 1e+010

:GRAPH NEW_CAPACITY
:TITLE new capacity
:SCALE
:VAR new capacity of wind turbines
:VAR new wind turbines capacity capacity
:VAR new wind turbines capacity capacity WF12

:GRAPH MONITORING_AND_CONTROL
:TITLE MONITORING_AND_CONTROL
:X-DIV 4
:X-MIN 2019
:X-MAX 2020
:SCALE
:VAR total capacity of installed wind turbines|total capacity of installed wind turbines (simulated)
:Y-MIN 1e+006
:Y-MAX 1.2e+006
:VAR total capacity WF12 report|total capacity WF12 report
:VAR real world capacity monitoring|real world capacity monitoring
:VAR total capacity of installed wind turbines|adapted total capacity of installed wind turbines
:DATASET sd1WF12_S1_monitoring_invalCapCap

:GRAPH GRAPH
:TITLE GRAPH
:SCALE
:VAR marginale kost nieuwe capaciteit T1
:VAR marginale kost nieuwe capaciteit T2
